background notes: The buss is a kind of ochebanian noble. It is the lowest rank and was introduced in 63 OW.
The matrio is a kind of ochebanian noble. Originally the lowest rank, it was second lowest from 63 OW on with the introduction of the buss.
The visduc is a kind of ochebanian noble standing between mardus and ducce.
The bisduc is a kind of ochebanian noble standing between ducce and corano.
The corano was the highest ochebanian noble.
The bichop was the highest official in the ochebanian clergy of Tempus. His noble rank was equal to that of a ducce.
The panne was a predominantly ochebanian helmet developed in 520 b. OW. It was very similar to real-world kettle hats.
The arteste was an ochebanian helmet developed in 450 b. OW. It was very similar to real-world nasal helmets.
The iffe was an ochebanian helmet developed in 320 b. OW used predominantly by noble's militias.
The faucette was a face-covering helmet very similar to real-world greathelms.
The roye was an ochebanian helmet developed in 5 b. OW.
The bukle was an ochebanian helmet used mainly for stylistic efect by soldiers from 89 OW. It looked very similar to real-world morions.
